#originalTopic=should-marriage-for-same-sex-couples-be-legal
Before Loving v. Virginia, marriage was the union between a man and a woman OF THE SAME RACE.Now, don't make the mistake of thinking that I'm equating   same-sex marriage   to interracial marriage. I'm just saying that the definition of marriage can and has evolved in the past.